Everything Instant Messaging Registry

Originally split between the Everything AIM Repository (a writeup created by [WonkoDSane] to index AOL Instant Messenger usernames) and the Everything ICQ Repository (a scheme nurtured by [yossarian]), this document has been reformatted to contain additional IM handles and contact information. It is now maintained by random e2gods.

TERMS OF USE

This document is provided expressly for the purpose of making public the information that account holders submit for inclusion in it, and the publisher offers NO GUARANTEES of confidentiality, either expressed or implied. While simple methods are undertaken to prevent robots from reading the e-mail addresses listed here, the publisher offers NO GUARANTEES that listed addresses will not be subjected to "spam" or other net abuse. Any information you submit for listing here is done so at your own risk, and the publisher is not responsible for any damages resulting from the accessibility of this information. If this page is indexed by search engines, its contents will be available as readily as anything else on the worldwide web.
